Package: blueskynet
Title: Analyze Networks on the Bluesky Social Network
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lasse", "Hjorth Madsen", , "lassehjorthmadsen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for generating and analyzing networks on Bluesky
    Social. Based on a given actor (user) on Bluesky, we can generate a
    network based on what users the actor followes. Outputs are a graph
    with information on who follows who among this set of actors, and a
    dataset with some metadata about the actors. Also included are a few
    tools from `igraph` and `tidygraph` for network analysis.
